  "body": "Some minor changes to this contract will make it much easier to use and understand:\r\n * A renaming may be in place, to better reflect that multiple payments are supported, and that this is a standalone contract (unlike `PullPayment`). Maybe `PaymentSplitter`? `MultiPayee` (a la `Multisig`)? `SplitPayments` has also been suggested.\r\n * `_addPayee` should be made `private`, since it is only used in the constructor (and the contract is not meant to be extended anyway)\r\n * We should emit `PayeeAdded(address)` (in `_addPayee`), `PaymentReleased(address, uint256)` (in `release`) and `PaymentReceived(uint256 amount)` events, to make it easier to analyse how the contract was used.",
